-Richie Sambora, Tico Torres and David Bryan along with the rest of Richie&#039;s live solo tour band rehearse for the short lived 1991 solo tour. They play solo stuff as well as a few unreleased cuts and songs Richie wrote for other artists. It&#039;s the final piece of the Sessions set, and comprises all known Bon Jovi and solo demos which have not been released as b-sides or otherwise in an official manner.

Pretty much all the 2nd/3rd... takes are just teeny little instrumental bits. I don&#039;t even know why they were included on the discs, but they were, so who am I to remove them? :)
